            "title": "Vertiv與EchoStar領漲標普500指數調整中的科技股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkDpYjpDmIaIJWpMGtgkUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA8400B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - S&amp;P Dow Jones Indices週五宣布對其基準追蹤指數進行全面調整,推動多家科技和工業公司進入備受矚目的標普500指數。Vertiv Holdings Co(NYSE:VRT)股價在盤後交易中飆升5.6%,而EchoStar Corporation(NASDAQ:SATS)和Lumentum Holdings Inc(NASDAQ:LITE)也錄得顯著漲幅。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f200a479-f2d3-3ba6-b83f-b5d8e2e9c414-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這次季度調整旨在維護市場最受關注指標的完整性。S&amp;P DJI表示,\"這些變動確保每個指數更能代表其市值範圍\",涵蓋大型股、中型股和小型股層級。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Vertiv、Lumentum、Coherent Inc(NYSE:COHR)和<span><span>EchoStar</span></span>將在3月23日週一開盤前正式加入標普500指數。為騰出空間容納這些新成員,該指數將剔除Match Group Inc(NASDAQ:MTCH)、Molina Healthcare Inc(NYSE:MOH)、Lamb Weston Holdings Inc(NYSE:LW)和Paycom(NYSE:PAYC)。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在更高層級,標普100指數將迎來半導體和工業巨頭的顯著加入,包括Micron Technology Inc(NASDAQ:MU)和GE Vernova LLC(NYSE:GEV)。這些調整將導致資深金融公司如PayPal Holdings Inc(NASDAQ:PYPL)和American International Group Inc(NYSE:AIG)退出這個藍籌股百強俱樂部。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者預計這些調整將觸發數十億美元的被動基金資金流動,因為機構管理者將重新調整其投資組合以符合新基準。生效日期分散在未來兩週內,首先從3月13日的SmallCap 600調整開始。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/vertiv%E8%88%87echostar%E9%A0%98%E6%BC%B2%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE500%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E8%82%A1-233634553.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 08:23:32",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
